{"tid":230312,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"Present continuous (future) vs will be doing","createTime":"2017-05-05T09:18:15.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-05T10:24:06.000Z","uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"2053e2b0b90e667b5539579b52fe0252c082c8bb","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:18:15.000Z","msg":"1, Don't phone between 7 and 8. We<strong> will be</strong> having a meeting. <br />\n<br />\n2, Don't phone between 7 and 8. We <strong>are </strong>having a meeting. <br />\n<br />\n想問有乜分別? 2係arrange 左 1係無?<br />\n求救<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad1004f32a31ec29b1ec47c78206e9cf618b7dc1","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"a8043de3e913b60e41e671fe746c41589321a157","tid":230312,"uid":44163,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:45:51.000Z","msg":"Will be 係用係事實<br />\nGoing to 係 prediction<br />\n<br />\n所以當你好肯定或做緊決定時用will be"},{"pid":"ee727b85402f27b4e25bb5497c8f62d6ec6cad28","tid":230312,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:46:28.000Z","msg":"假設MEETING既時間點係將來<br />\n咁就應該如你所講<br />\nare having基本上係confirm左一定發生"},{"pid":"a31835349589473829aa4a62b2c8eb57a8e48b7e","tid":230312,"uid":44163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:46:42.000Z","msg":"Btw善用google"},{"pid":"e4b2751aebd72dbf439bafbfe49e73b42e109053","tid":230312,"uid":24310,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:50:47.000Z","msg":"9up<br />\n<br />\n第一個 (time before 7) 提醒人唔好打黎 因為嗰時會開緊會<br />\n<br />\n第二個 (time between 7-8) 開緊會有人打黎 提醒人唔好再打黎"},{"pid":"46b5bb6a527d567a7b632c668d458cc6949f60b7","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:53:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Will be 係用係事實<br />\nGoing to 係 prediction<br />\n<br />\n所以當你好肯定或做緊決定時用will be</blockquote><br />\n多謝你覆我<br />\n我明going to 係有prediction既意思  <br />\n但Present continuous (future) 唔係講你決定左/計劃左既野咩? 換句話講佢既發生既可能性唔係應該係比will be高咩?"},{"pid":"c4136f0d2aade1b257efe474e526455a06460955","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:57:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>假設MEETING既時間點係將來<br />\n咁就應該如你所講<br />\nare having基本上係confirm左一定發生</blockquote><br />\n你意思係 一樣講將來<br />\nPresent continuous 係已經plan左<br />\nwill be doing係應該會做緊某樣野?<br />\n可能性 will be 係會比較低?咁樣?"},{"pid":"b00c81f3537cecf867873f2a5d99e8e37310293a","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T09:58:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>9up<br />\n<br />\n第一個 (time before 7) 提醒人唔好打黎 因為嗰時會開緊會<br />\n<br />\n第二個 (time between 7-8) 開緊會有人打黎 提醒人唔好再打黎</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n點解你會有咁既理解既?<br />\n可唔可以詳細小小話我知?"},{"pid":"fbf6f2edfef94b6cb283069d65f478efd8efc681","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:04:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw善用google</blockquote><br />\n我查完都唔係好明所以先上黎問可能我理解力唔係咁好<br />\n唔好意思啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11275cf62bbea24e64eeb5b6bf2600a2edc434a6","tid":230312,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"Be going to係講之前一早plan好<br />\nWill係講個下先決定<br />\nWill be後面通常都會跟時間詞 particular time<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">學英文 Google好過開post問</span>"},{"pid":"3684ce70818c0e6de3a70aeded6144dfa1a3fe88","tid":230312,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:08:58.000Z","msg":"Btw學好英文先學日文啦"},{"pid":"946de9d3cac6200522435a637fdaee591879e2b7","tid":230312,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>假設MEETING既時間點係將來<br />\n咁就應該如你所講<br />\nare having基本上係confirm左一定發生</blockquote><br />\n你意思係 一樣講將來<br />\nPresent continuous 係已經plan左<br />\nwill be doing係應該會做緊某樣野?<br />\n可能性 will be 係會比較低?咁樣?</blockquote><br />\nwill be係比較低<br />\n你用present cont' 黎描述未來既事，即係件事已經確定左99%會做，同時件事係有持續性"},{"pid":"3856e10f53d566b22955b1f21e42a06e5db42726","tid":230312,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:14:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.ef.com/english-resources/english-grammar/present-continuous/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.ef.com%2Fenglish-resources%2Fenglish-grammar%2Fpresent-continuous%2F&d=xEw7bVcEuEkne8wYN5Y7CviMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=6d5f2071\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.ef.com/english-resources/english-grammar/present-continuous/</a>"},{"pid":"d65620dd0c01ae6e74b9b95f398d940d622dea1f","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:17:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw學好英文先學日文啦</blockquote><br />\n係日本住所以點都要學小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daaee56b87dae0ed2befe1137a286f6d18747acf","tid":230312,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:17:29.000Z","msg":"簡而言之：<br />\nWill vs be v-ing: 強調「決定」<br />\n<br />\nWill be v-ing: 某段時間進行中既事<br />\n-&gt; 所以多數跟specific time frame / event去突顯個刻發生緊動作。否則意思含混(=/=錯）<br />\n<br />\n回應你例子：<br />\nWill be having meeting in between 7-8<br />\n-&gt; 陣間7-8開緊會。（一定發生）<br />\n-&gt; 強調event呢件事<br />\n<br />\nAre having meeting in between 7-8<br />\n-&gt; 計劃好7-8點會開緊會。（係咪一定？，呢個用法邏輯睇唔到，因為佢強調說話呢一刻）<br />\n-&gt; 強調呢刻決定<br />\n-&gt; it is predictable they are preparing things for the meeting"},{"pid":"ab11121f68dcdb05a8a1deca493a59696da01045","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:17:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>假設MEETING既時間點係將來<br />\n咁就應該如你所講<br />\nare having基本上係confirm左一定發生</blockquote><br />\n你意思係 一樣講將來<br />\nPresent continuous 係已經plan左<br />\nwill be doing係應該會做緊某樣野?<br />\n可能性 will be 係會比較低?咁樣?</blockquote><br />\nwill be係比較低<br />\n你用present cont' 黎描述未來既事，即係件事已經確定左99%會做，同時件事係有持續性</blockquote><br />\n感謝 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  明白啦"},{"pid":"288b47e9e64e7560188937d30717353551eba83b","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:17:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>簡而言之：<br />\nWill vs be v-ing: 強調「決定」<br />\n<br />\nWill be v-ing: 某段時間進行中既事<br />\n-&gt; 所以多數跟specific time frame / event去突顯個刻發生緊動作。否則意思含混(=/=錯）<br />\n<br />\n回應你例子：<br />\nWill be having meeting in between 7-8<br />\n-&gt; 陣間7-8開緊會。（一定發生）<br />\n-&gt; 強調event呢件事<br />\n<br />\nAre having meeting in between 7-8<br />\n-&gt; 計劃好7-8點會開緊會。（係咪一定？，呢個用法邏輯睇唔到，因為佢強調說話呢一刻）<br />\n-&gt; 強調呢刻決定<br />\n-&gt; it is predictable they are preparing things for the meeting</blockquote><br />\n多謝你好詳細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a93aff2439578c12e97ccf5390e0ac046c88deb1","tid":230312,"uid":192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:18:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>Btw學好英文先學日文啦</blockquote><br />\n係日本住所以點都要學小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rich"},{"pid":"74526fb6228f8b460a54285b7e5a0957ea28cd11","tid":230312,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:20:40.000Z","msg":"兩句帶出既意思上係唔同<br />\n<br />\n因為前者：描述緊7-8點開緊會，呢件事<br />\n<br />\n因為後者：描述緊傳話者有7-8點開會呢個決定，並應該準備緊相關工作"},{"pid":"665e74e87776da0183c26cbb947d0ca129ab0fa6","tid":230312,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:22:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>Btw學好英文先學日文啦</blockquote><br />\n係日本住所以點都要學小小<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rich</blockquote><br />\n唔係啦 不過係呢邊真係無乜機會操英文 啲老師既英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  但日文就日日都要講 講到聽得明就算 無乜特別放好多時間落去 反而想操英文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6295302995c6992654c0332a832ed15bc72cdabe","tid":230312,"uid":29929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-05T10:24:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>假設MEETING既時間點係將來<br />\n咁就應該如你所講<br />\nare having基本上係confirm左一定發生</blockquote><br />\n你意思係 一樣講將來<br />\nPresent continuous 係已經plan左<br />\nwill be doing係應該會做緊某樣野?<br />\n可能性 will be 係會比較低?咁樣?</blockquote><br />\nwill be係比較低<br />\n你用present cont' 黎描述未來既事，即係件事已經確定左99%會做，同時件事係有持續性</blockquote><br />\nWill be v-ing 唔存在可能性啦<br />\n<br />\n因為佢直接大前題已經將時間線拉到個陣發生緊咩事，形容緊個陣有咩做"}]}